'''Lizil''' was the name of a hive inhabited by the [[Killik/Legends|Killik]] [[Lizil (Hive)|Lizils]]. It was contained within an [[Asteroid/Legends|asteroid]] in the [[Unknown Regions/Legends|Unknown Regions]].

==History==
[[Han Solo/Legends|Han]] and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] as well as [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke]] and [[Mara Jade Skywalker]] first met the [[Lizil (Hive)|Lizil]] hive here when they were searching for the members of the [[Myrkr strike team]] in the [[Unknown Regions/Legends|Unknown Regions]]. It was at this hive that the Solos first met [[Jae Juun]] and [[Tarfang]].

Later, the Solos encountered the [[Squib/Legends|Squibs]] [[Grees]], [[Sligh]], and [[Emala]] selling weapons to the Lizil here.

